'''"Sleepy" Nagelson''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] who had earned his nickname while flying a reconnaissance mission during the [[Thrawn campaign]] while asleep. He was sent to fly a recon through the [[Star system/Legends|star system]] that contained [[Wakiza]] and did not return; it was speculated that he was either shot down or captured by the [[Yevetha]].

